I top ticked OXY to the day boy. My ytd rivals all those accounts that been spamming Photonics and all those AI supply chain stocks. Yet I never owned any of those AI plays. Missing out on Bloom Energy hurts my heart after pumping it earlier much in the year. I could have been talking more shit against all those AI guys if I longed it but it’s whatever 😂, being able to have a return match the AI peddlers on this platform without any of their AI exposure, feels good in it of itself. I don’t have Serenity’s return though that dude is killing it, but I legit have zero influence in being able to pump stocks. If people actually listened to me and followed my plays I would crush his return too I believe 😂. Some can be turned off by my competitiveness but this is a zero sum game. Kill or be eaten. I didn’t make the rules, but ima play the game to not just win, but to dominate. I only feel good when it’s a blow out."}}}, "quoted_status_result": {"result": {"__typename": "Tweet", "core": {"user_results": {"result": {"__typename": "User", "affiliates_highlighted_label": {}, "avatar": {"image_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1263065756511670272/nsbajEq-_normal.jpg"}, "core": {"created_at": "Mon Jan 22 11:57:09 +0000 2018", "name": "LordPos3idon", "screen_name": "LordPos3idon"}, "dm_permissions": {"can_dm": true}, "follow_request_sent": false, "has_graduated_access": true, "id": "VXNlcjo5NTU0MDg5OTM4NTc1MzE5MDQ=", "is_blue_verified": true, "legacy": {"default_profile": true, "default_profile_image": false, "description": "•Words are the derivatives of experience •Head of Global Macro @ Axe Capital •Geopolitical Asshole •Slytherin Alumni •Lisan Al Gaib •Sith Lord •Ruler of the Sea", "entities": {"description": {}}, "fast_followers_count": 0, "favourites_count": 16429, "follow_request_sent": false, "followers_count": 1560, "friends_count": 2207, "has_custom_timelines": false, "is_translator": false, "listed_count": 23, "media_count": 2394, "needs_phone_verification": false, "normal_followers_count": 1560, "notifications": false, "pinned_tweet_ids_str": ["1934838193490215194"], "possibly_sensitive": false, "profile_banner_url": "", "profile_interstitial_type": "", "statuses_count": 11881, "time_zone": "", "translator_type": "none", "url": "", "utc_offset": 0, "want_retweets": false, "withheld_description": "", "withheld_scope": ""}, "location": {"location": "New York, NY"}, "media_permissions": {"can_media_tag": true}, "parody_commentary_fan_label": "None", "privacy": {"protected": false}, "profile_bio": {"description": "•Words are the derivatives of experience •Head of Global Macro @ Axe Capital •Geopolitical Asshole •Slytherin Alumni •Lisan Al Gaib •Sith Lord •Ruler of the Sea"}, "profile_description_language": "en", "profile_image_shape": "Circle", "relationship_perspectives": {"blocked_by": false, "blocking": false, "followed_by": false, "following": false, "muting": false}, "rest_id": "955408993857531904", "super_follow_eligible": false, "super_followed_by": false, "super_following": false, "verification": {"verified": false}}}}, "edit_control": {"edit_tweet_ids": ["2038698870650380340"], "editable_until_msecs": "1774902262000", "edits_remaining": "5", "is_edit_eligible": true}, "grok_analysis_button": true, "is_translatable": false, "legacy": {"bookmark_count": 0, "bookmarked": false, "conversation_id_str": "2038698870650380340", "created_at": "Mon Mar 30 19:24:22 +0000 2026", "display_text_range": [0, 279], "entities": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "timestamps": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": []}, "favorite_count": 1, "favorited": false, "full_text": "I sold these April OXY calls for 9x. Not as sweet as the 22x I made on the OXY call spreads I had for March, but still a nice diabetic sweet. Still gonna hold the OXY stock that I have, but all the convexity for this name is gone, shit, all the convexity for Oil futures to me is", "id_str": "2038698870650380340", "is_quote_status": true, "lang": "en", "quote_count": 1, "quoted_status_id_str": "2029617831474581558", "quoted_status_permalink": {"display": "x.com/LordPos3idon/s…", "expanded": "https://twitter.com/LordPos3idon/status/2029617831474581558", "url": "https://t.co/pORRnTbD3u"}, "reply_count": 0, "retweet_count": 0, "retweeted": false, "user_id_str": "955408993857531904"}, "note_tweet": {"is_expandable": true, "note_tweet_results": {"result": {"entity_set": {"hashtags": [], "symbols": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": []}, "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwMzg2OTg4NzA1NTgwNjg3MzY=", "text": "I sold these April OXY calls for 9x. Not as sweet as the 22x I made on the OXY call spreads I had for March, but still a nice diabetic sweet. Still gonna hold the OXY stock that I have, but all the convexity for this name is gone, shit, all the convexity for Oil futures to me is GONE. Oil is going to languish here for a while, and the easy money has been made already. I squeezed out all the juice I could from OXY. The other options in the repost are worthless but they’re not even a mosquito bite in terms of what it did to my PnL because of how successfully I rode OXY YTD here man. Those other options still have time left, in case the Hormuz situation explodes, but I’m not banking on that, hence why I am selling OXY, despite them having 3 weeks til expiration left. Still holding NEXT stock as well. This market is a LONG"}}}, "quotedRefResult": {"result": {"__typename": "Tweet", "rest_id": "2029617831474581558"}}, "rest_id": "2038698870650380340", "source": "<a href="http://twitter.com/download/iphone" rel="nofollow">Twitter for iPhone</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "504", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}}, "rest_id": "2044157093767446797", "source": "<a href="http://twitter.com/download/iphone" rel="nofollow">Twitter for iPhone</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "240", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

