@aleabitoreddit Your bottleneck-of-the-bottleneck tactic led me to tiny $CVV (~$30M cap).  

Their CVD/PVT systems grow SiC crystals + epi layers for AI power electronics &amp; InP/GaAs photonics.  
Western moat. Am I onto the smth?

